    "description": "Lift Attendant is a minimalist puzzle game where you control elevators to transport passengers to their destinations. Your objective is to transport passengers as efficiently as possible. Earn money based on your efficiency and use money to upgrade your elevators to further improve efficiency!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Levels to Unlock</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/4e20619a6947f3b83315a045f793ac31.poster.avif?t=1722441506\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/4e20619a6947f3b83315a045f793ac31.webm?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/4e20619a6947f3b83315a045f793ac31.mp4?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each level has a predefined passenger spawn pattern and failure conditions, so you can continue to replay each level as many times as you'd like and try to get a better score each time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Elevators</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/fed0d06a978e39d65fb5ead92bfc5d9c.poster.avif?t=1722441506\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/fed0d06a978e39d65fb5ead92bfc5d9c.webm?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/fed0d06a978e39d65fb5ead92bfc5d9c.mp4?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your earned money to upgrade your elevators to move faster and also hold additional passengers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Queue Floors to Plan Ahead</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/079e8bf6a46fbe429d660681d88e265b.poster.avif?t=1722441506\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/079e8bf6a46fbe429d660681d88e265b.webm?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/079e8bf6a46fbe429d660681d88e265b.mp4?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Elevators will always be boarded to full capacity by passengers on the floor they stop on. This means you can see which floors your elevator will need to travel to. Use this to your advantage and plan ahead by queuing the floors ahead of time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Elevators</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/c2ed356457c237e65521e4c23290776d.poster.avif?t=1722441506\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/c2ed356457c237e65521e4c23290776d.webm?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/c2ed356457c237e65521e4c23290776d.mp4?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>One elevator is often not enough. Improve efficiency by upgrading to additional elevators and further optimize your passenger transporting strategy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Passenger Patience</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/ccb65bccf9ecadec3cd7a6b94c77b7a9.poster.avif?t=1722441506\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/ccb65bccf9ecadec3cd7a6b94c77b7a9.webm?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/ccb65bccf9ecadec3cd7a6b94c77b7a9.mp4?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Passengers have a limited amount of patience. Keep passengers happy by transporting them as quickly as possible. The happier they are, the more money you earn.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Efficiency Bonuses</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/f65cc2fed382783c55b9174593eae2d7.poster.avif?t=1722441506\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/f65cc2fed382783c55b9174593eae2d7.webm?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/f65cc2fed382783c55b9174593eae2d7.mp4?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Transport multiple passengers to the same floor for efficiency bonuses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Track High Scores</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/0df10cec9c4bf0a8d02f7492a066eca8.poster.avif?t=1722441506\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/0df10cec9c4bf0a8d02f7492a066eca8.webm?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035940/extras/0df10cec9c4bf0a8d02f7492a066eca8.mp4?t=1722441506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Feel like you can do better next time? Your high scores are tracked and you can always revisit a level to try and beat your previous score.",
